TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Competitive Pricing Model
AU  - Mesak, Hani I.
AU  - Clelland, Richard C.
Y1  - 1979/11/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.25.11.1057
